----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job Description 1 :

Role Overview:
We are looking for a transformation expert to lead our legacy modernization initiatives. You will be responsible for conducting a comprehensive current state IT assessment to identify bottlenecks in our application landscape. Your primary goal is to define the target architecture definition that supports our future digital business models.

Key Skills:
Current state IT assessment, Application landscape understanding, Target architecture definition, Legacy system rationalization, Technology risk identification.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job Description 2 :

- Lead the development of the IT strategy and roadmap for a large financial institution.
- Prioritize technology initiatives based on business value and feasibility.
- Define the technology vision definition for the next 3-5 years.
- Evaluate the risks associated with major technology investments.

Skills:
Technology vision definition, Roadmap sequencing, Initiative prioritization, Feasibility evaluation, Risk evaluation.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job Description 3 :

The Opportunity:
You will drive cloud adoption for enterprise clients. This involves evaluating cloud versus on-premise tradeoffs and selecting the right mix of providers (AWS, Azure, GCP). You must provide workload suitability reasoning for moving critical applications to the cloud and ensure clients avoid vendor lock-in risks.

Required Skills:
Cloud adoption approach, Cloud versus on premise tradeoffs, Cloud provider evaluation, Workload suitability reasoning, Vendor lock in risk awareness.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

